Gambas program to make a calculator.
The UI (User Interface) can be made according to the user's needs.



' Gambas class file

Public c As Integer
Public Sub _new()
c = 0
End

Public Sub Form_Open()

End

Public Sub Number_KeyPress()

  

End

Public Sub Check_Click()
  c = CInt(Number.Text)
  If c % 2 == 0 Then
    Message.Info("Even Number")
  Else
    Message.Info("Odd Number")  
  Endif

End

